studyArms.name: Group 1: upadacitinib 15 mg QD
studyArms.description: Subjects receive upadacitinib 15 mg once daily for the duration of the study.

studyArms.name: Group 2: upadacitinib 30 mg QD
studyArms.description: Subjects receive upadacitinib 30 mg once daily. Note: Per Amendment 8, subjects on 30mg will be switched to 15mg at their next visit.

studyArms.name: Group 3: Placebo followed by upadacitinib 15 mg QD
studyArms.description: Subjects receive placebo for the first 24 weeks, then switch to upadacitinib 15 mg once daily.

studyArms.name: Group 4: Placebo followed by upadacitinib 30 mg QD
studyArms.description: Subjects receive placebo for the first 24 weeks, then switch to upadacitinib 30 mg once daily.

studyCohorts.name: Bio-IR
studyCohorts.characteristic: Subjects with moderately to severely active Psoriatic Arthritis who have an inadequate response to at least one biologic DMARD
